Depends: ruby, curl, libcurl, make, clang, build-essential
Section: ruby
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/taf2/curb
Description: Ruby bindings for libcurl
 Curb provides Ruby bindings for the libcurl HTTP client library.
 It allows full control over HTTP requests, cookies, and sessions.
